---
title: Falafel Rainbow Wraps with Quick-Pickled Onions and Lemony Hummus
description: This wrap is bursting with fresh flavour! Filling falafel, zesty hummus and a whole bunch of wholesome veggies get wrapped in warm flatbread for a delicious dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/wraps-aux-falafels-arc-en-ciel-0122d39b.jpg
